Z","msg":"瘋狗症一病發的話，死亡率過100%....<br />\n支針係毒你唔死，不過最終比瘋狗症病發死"},{"pid":"c62966d915d731496d66db288582841c108ada6f","tid":753763,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f688c8beeedc905d9d4c0b76b9e0a1c41c7866e6","tid":753763,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eef66a21330d3743b5d519e8e38256fa3e280fd4","tid":753763,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abc5e8a7043a47e28a9eb518a6aad1f45dab3684","tid":753763,"uid":35914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:50:12.000Z","msg":"D貨無事但要改紀錄係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:56:45.000Z","msg":"佢而家解釋話半支當1支 係唔夠料，<br />\n但係唔會毒死妳wo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"瘋狗症一病發的話，死亡率過100%....<br />\n支針係毒你唔死，不過最終比瘋狗症病發死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:11:51.000Z","msg":"係近100%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068b4d34d94d9a3da55aaec14b17add99884b42d","tid":753763,"uid":28309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:12:22.000Z","msg":"即場自啪返支囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4bf0d2c73579ee440b234c0868159c1b6cc7ca","tid":753763,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"聽住先啦"},{"pid":"e09f76a926a95c342f75218c1bfb373d4a9ad77e","tid":753763,"uid":22913,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:13:13.000Z","msg":"kay事件香港專家都差唔多<br />\n藥效不夠仍然值得注射"},{"pid":"75123f7fda1b0efb245fe5c3314a2a235618a7ab","tid":753763,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:14:35.000Z","msg":"我啲貨堅野黎, 不過我屎忽痕改吓紀錄啫<br />\n一定係咁"},{"pid":"bde0178e6c32771917e65ed3e2a5ddb3ecf5df13","tid":753763,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:17:41.000Z","msg":"叫你個孫/親友 即場打返幾枝先講"},{"pid":"04e706d3e86b3dd4a40656b198d23a901a2a2dec","tid":753763,"uid":129235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abc5e8a7043a47e28a9eb518a6aad1f45dab3684","tid":753763,"uid":35914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:50:12.000Z","msg":"D貨無事但要改紀錄係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:26:09.000Z","msg":"怕D 貨太傑出太優質全世界都來搶購，到時支那小孩就無得打，所以要改紀錄，用心良苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095f4b58a282a9051503c7e1695db35f9f1d9fd4","tid":753763,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾貨改假數據就聽過<br />\n堅野改做垃圾真係第一次聽"},{"pid":"26b4180f3584581155ada27266b40ce8cbd51d91","tid":753763,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:34:33.000Z","msg":"他又說，「效價不符合標準」是「劣藥」問題，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「疫苗是安全的，只是有效劑量不夠，會影響疫苗接種的效果」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2005年，山東省一名男子注射長春長生狂犬疫苗後，導致雙眼幾乎失明，右眼無光感，右眼視力剩0.1。但是，最後長生公司沒有提供疫苗檢驗合格證明，仍舊被判無責。<br />\n<br />\n2007年，山西發生多起兒童注射疫苗致殘致死案，但相關事件被當局隱瞞、壓制，直至2010年曝光。而涉事的北京華衛時代公司改名為華夏德眾，繼續經營，直到2016年再爆風波。<br />\n<br />\n2008年，江蘇延申對狂犬疫苗數據進行修改，違規替換抽檢樣品。<br />\n<br />\n2009年，大連金港安迪非法向狂犬疫苗添加核酸物質；同年，河北福爾、江蘇延申的狂犬疫苗，總共7個批次、21.58萬人份的疫苗存質量問題。<br />\n<br />\n2013年，康泰生物、北京天壇、大連漢信，多地發生嬰兒死亡疑似跟接種疫苗有關，調查結果則是指死亡與疫苗無關。<br />\n<br />\n2016年，山東兆信、山東寶傑等9家公司被爆出，在18各省市疫苗經營和運輸者，在此前的6年間，大量供應無效或過期疫苗，涉及金額高達5.7億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n2017年，中國有兩家疫苗生產公司共計65萬多支「百白破」疫苗不符合標準，分別是：長春長生批次為201605014-01的「百日破」，和武漢生物批號為201607050- 2的問題疫苗。其中長春長生有25萬支假疫苗流入山東，或涉及25萬戶家庭；武漢生物40萬隻問題疫苗，其中19萬支流向重慶，21萬支流向河北。"},{"pid":"b06c1b59b7e2bbbbf2e213e41982139fd8cbe4a8","tid":753763,"uid":54142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e991f17358f95a35f82274dfff3bd77ae2dd227","tid":753763,"uid":10823,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:44:18.000Z","msg":"性價比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人命啊 健康啊<br />\n佢同你講性價比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係笑撚左<br />\n唔駛問 笑撚埋右"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:42:50.000Z","msg":"中國沒錢就不是人類<br />\n無產階級就是蟲子般存在"},{"pid":"c41be23a7ace7bfc625224987d9261aec414ca57","tid":753763,"uid":64193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:46:17.000Z","msg":"疫苗無效咁仲打黎把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecccb0e2975c5a638d8a1da7982d8cb5f978f24","tid":753763,"uid":65263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c41be23a7ace7bfc625224987d9261aec414ca57","tid":753763,"uid":64193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:46:17.000Z","msg":"疫苗無效咁仲打黎把鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T04:23:41.000Z","msg":"心靈慰藉"},{"pid":"d090473a2ed09a47423d51c84a7941f8bb9a7744","tid":753763,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"支国有邊一日唔係做假先係新聞"},{"pid":"ae5f920e6657ba2c4eac675ddd05d352ab783d1d","tid":753763,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T04:46:49.000Z","msg":"支那專家同共媒真係好正 你地阿頭都知大穫冚唔住啦 仲係到妖言惑眾"}]}